(START)
   |
   |
   v
[Load data from database.json]
   |
   |
   v
{Does database exist and load correctly?}
   |Yes                    |No
   v                       v
[Use loaded data]     [Create empty database]
                           |
                           |
                           v
                   [Save empty database]
                           |
                           |
                           v
<Display Main Menu>
   |
   |
   v
<Enter user choice>
   |
   |
   v
{Is choice between 1 and 6?}
   |Yes                     |No
   v                        v
{Is choice = 6?}        <Display error message>
   |Yes        |No            |
   v           v              |
[Save database]   {Choice = 1?}◄──────────────┘
   |               |Yes   |No
   v               v      v
 (END)          [Add Item] {Choice = 2?}
                           |Yes    |No
                           v       v
                       [View DB] {Choice = 3?}
                                  |Yes   |No
                                  v      v
                              [Update Item] {Choice = 4?}
                                             |Yes   |No
                                             v      v
