UPDATE_ITEM_FLOWCHART

(START UPDATE)
   |
   |
   v
<Enter item ID>
   |
   |
   v
{Does ID exist in database?}
   |Yes                    |No
   v                       v
<Enter attribute to change> <Display "ID not found">
   |
   |
   v                       |
{Is attribute valid?}◄─────┘
   |Yes      |No
   v         v
<Enter new value>   <Display error message>
   |
   |
   v
[Update item in database]
   |
   |
   v
[Save database]
   |
   |
   v
(Return to menu)


